 asteroid hit the town? Pooling these loans into a securitization dulls the=
 impact of these exogenous, binary risks and increases an investor&#8217;s =
confidence that they will, in aggregate, perform according to the underwrit=
ten expectations. As a rule of thumb, </span><strong>the higher an investor=
&#8217;s degree of confidence in the outcome, the lower the returns one wil=
l demand</strong><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong>Standardization (=
&#8220;Narrow Waist&#8221;)</strong></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4=
