px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0; margin-left: 1em;"><em>If you wan=
t many, many things to be able to interoperate with many, many other things=
, there needs to be a narrow waist that is as constrained as possible betwe=
en them.</em></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0; margin-left: 1em;"><em><span>-</span><strong>Alex =
Danco</strong></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>Securitization is a form=
